review_data: Reviewed in the United States on March 7, 2021
name: JayN
title: Good value
review: I don't eat a lot of yogurt so I usually buy the single serve for anywhere from $0.99 to $1.49.This size tub is usually $7.99 at the grocery store.Got it here for $4.99 so the value for the larger size could not be beat.Was worried it would have an expiration date in the near future that would not allow me to use the whole tub, but happily the expiration date is more than 30 days away.Thumbs up.

review: This is the best yogurt I've had. It's non fat but thicc as a greek yogurt should be. In other brands non fat yogurts tend to be watery. This should be the 5th pint of the same brand that I ordered.
